captions.text: Take the elevator to your room by saying 'room'.
You will now be transported to the 9th floor.
On the 9th floor we have a complimentary photo shoot.

- Are you in a hurry?
- Yes!

For 1st floor, say one. For 2nd floor say two. For 3rd floor say 
 three. For 4th floor say four. For 5th floor say five ...

- For the 8th floor, say 'eight'. For 9th, say 'nine'.
- THREE!
